<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_98b6f526d292.aspx"><b>国风·周南·芣苢</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson98b6f526d292">
<p>采采芣苢，薄言采之。<br />采采芣苢，薄言有之。<br />采采芣苢，薄言掇之。<br />采采芣苢，薄言捋之。<br />采采芣苢，薄言袺之。<br />采采芣苢，薄言襭之。</p>
</div>
</div>
